// Dial content unchanged from the existing (rotation-corrected, pattern-verified) 410x410 crop -
// only the format changed, from opaque RGB565 to RGB565+alpha, so the 4 corner triangles outside
// the inscribed bezel circle (previously solid black, redundant against a black canvas) are now
// genuinely transparent. This lets the new face_citizen_410_body_bg layer show through in those
// corners instead of being hidden behind an opaque black square. Circle boundary measured directly
// off this same asset (radial scan from centre (205,205), median radius 205.0 across 360 samples,
// matches the canvas half-width as expected since the dial was originally scaled to fill it exactly)
// with a 1.5px feathered alpha falloff at the edge to avoid a hard-edged seam.

